    "display_name": "Digital Forensics Analyst",
    "long_instructions": " ## Digital Forensics Analyst\r\n\r\nA **digital forensics analyst** investigates cyber incidents by collecting and analyzing digital evidence to uncover how an attack happened and who was responsible.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Chat with the digital forensics analyst about your scenario. Figure out how the threat works and what harm it can cause.\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> A major hospital experienced a security breach that locked access to all patient records, lab results and appointment systems. The hospital was instructed by hackers to pay $5 million in Bitcoin within 72 hours or lose all their data. Based on this scenario, how does a ransomware attack work and why is it harmful?\r\n\r\n:::\r\n\r\n2. Chat with the digital forensics analyst about **ways to prevent ransomware attacks.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> What are ways to prevent ransomware attacks?\r\n:::\r\n \r\n3. Chat with the digital forensics analyst about **ways to prevent ransomware attacks using AI.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How can AI help detect early signs of a ransomware attack before it starts?*\r\n> - *Can AI analyze file activity patterns to spot potential ransomware behavior?*\r\n> - *How does AI assist in blocking phishing emails that often deliver ransomware?*\r\n:::\r\n\r\n4. Chat with the digital forensics analyst about **ways that AI can make ransomware attacks more harmful.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How might bad actors use AI in cyberattacks, and what does that mean for defenders?*\r\n> - *How does AI change the threat landscape for ransomware as a cyber threat?*\r\n:::",
